      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BAROOGA JIM (6) is racing well without winning, recording three minors on end, the latest hitting the ground running with a fast early sectional but finishing in the minors again when second (30.05) over 525m at The Meadows. Key chance in this line up. PAW PALMER (4) produced an impressive win last time in quickest of the meeting when scoring by 5.5 lengths (22.75) at Horsham. Expected to feature again. PAW RAYNOR (8) has a fair record and proved too strong last time to win by a neck at Ballarat in a handy 25.19 beating Biscottino. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. Should be in this for a long way. REUBEN HILL (3) generally performs well from this box.",
